    Page: 80
    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Death
---
It is through death, the daily dying, that the soul has a gradual rising to
the consciousness of God. It is a gradual liberation and self-discovery of
the divine germ within the self. Physical death is an insignificant thing,
about as significant as the breaking of a string.
